Package com.ultreon.craft.server.player

Class ServerPlayer

java.lang.Object
com.ultreon.craft.entity.Entity
com.ultreon.craft.entity.LivingEntity
com.ultreon.craft.entity.Player
com.ultreon.craft.server.player.ServerPlayer
All Implemented Interfaces:
CommandSender, CacheablePlayer
public non-sealed class ServerPlayer extends Player implements CacheablePlayer
Server-side player implementation. Represents an online player.

NOTE: Should not be stored in collections, if you need to store a player in a collection. You should get the cached player instead,

See Also:
  • UltracraftServer.getCachedPlayer(String)
